{
  "stem": "8423.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So very often, we did not eat our own bread, and stole some when we could, and bring it to the people in our barracks, you know, that we're starving all the time.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These women, the three women.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, just two, Lucy and Emma.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The other one went with the workers to the factories.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- we would not let them see us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I tell you something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't say they were nice, and I was never beaten by them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, one was actually a giggler, and the other was always smiling, which was uncanny.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the two chefs, the two ladies, who they find out later on was no chefs, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they knew right away that she was a professional opera singer, Marta, as soon as she open her mouth, you know, and they liked her very much to sing.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had some kind of a relationship with them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a matter of-- oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they have found out that the head woman, Marta, had a birthday, and they've been saving from the rations to make a party for her with a cake and everything.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And some of the kids, like myself, were asked to entertain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I did the Csardas with my sister and a couple of kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we put on a little show for them, after the men were all, you know, tucked away so they were no place around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was just the two women in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were appreciative of the fact that these women were decent.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
